{"tid":1164751,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖)覺唔覺D毒撚又矮又肥又柒, 仲要成日著住件死人波衫, 真係柒毒上加柒毒?","createTime":"2019-05-21T10:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T10:39:01.000Z","uid":157483,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d83e66855793743aad6e0c1d20962644cbf3796c","tid":1164751,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T10:24:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾, 鍾意睇波唔撚係問題, 但鍾意睇波到成日FF自己係個球星, 又要驚死人唔知著埋出黎比人睇 真係好撚柒啊<br />\nfine, 如果你身材好既 carry到件衫 著得型咁, 寫個服字比你, 但屌你老尾又矮又肥又毒<br />\nd肥矮毒撚著波衫根本就係自己鞭緊自己屍, 你著住件C朗波衫, 人地自然會諗起C朗, 185高大型棍, 再望撚住你條柒頭165又肥又矮又柒, 對比之下, 簡直係視覺既衝擊, 粗暴無情、活生生既鞭屍示眾<br />\n次次見到D死肥矮毒撚著住件波衫, 仲面露自豪之色, 真係忍唔住笑<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/12/41/10124101_196559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F12%2F41%2F10124101_196559.jpg&h=b1ede813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/yh16Q.ADbyBe9WLj_KSo7Q--~B/aD02Mzg7dz00NDU7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/219144.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fyh16Q.ADbyBe9WLj_KSo7Q--~B%2FaD02Mzg7dz00NDU7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F219144.jpg&h=23e98866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/aug/12/images/bigPic/600_166.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Faug%2F12%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F600_166.jpg&h=614dedfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/hgkI2l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FhgkI2l.jpg&h=005b01a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/krohBF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FkrohBF.jpg&h=76d6379a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140312/la